data.text:
30% SATIVA - 60% INDICA - 10% RUDERALIS

THC: 21,00% CBD: 0,50% CBN: 0,10%

Genetics

Blue Haze x Gelato 41 Auto

Effects

Good balance between mental and body high, perfect as a “all day” strain.

Flowering Indoor

9-10 weeks of flowering.

11 weeks total crop time.

Yield Indoor

Medium.

Flowering Outdoor

11 weeks of flowering.

Yield Outdoor

100g/Plant

Description

This beautiful strain is the result of a careful selection of Blue Haze, which was crossed with Gelato #41 Auto-flowering.

The result is a very fragrant plant that expresses both Haze and Gelato characters. The effects are well balanced and appreciated by all consumers. Flavors range from sour, lemony, sweet, and even gassy.

The plant is very nice and compact, and because of the haze genes, this plant tends to be slightly taller than the other crosses of Gelato #41 Auto. Indoors, this plant can produce up to 500g/m2 if grown correctly, with a height of 100/140 cm. Outdoors it is also very resistant and can produce up to 80/100g per plant.

This genetic is characterized by medium node spacing and good number of branches. The flowers are elongated and full of trichomes, with colors ranging from dark green to purple.

The most expressed terpenes are D-Limonene, β-Caryophyllene and α-Humulene
